Text: Re Matchcom Youve Got Mail HelloHi Paul Thanks for the email so tell me more Marlene From To Subject Matchcom Youve Got Mail Hello Date Mon Dec Hello I saw your picture on the web site and I thought Id drop you a line I sent along my profile Take a look and see if there is any interest If there is Id like to hear from you Paul Click the following link to view the senders profile doubleblindshowprofileaspUserIDCBEtrackingid The following is my profile text Hello Im a down to earth person that likes to laugh and have a good time I work in downtown Denver as a commodities trader for a large energy trading house I do enjoy my career but understand life needs to be kept in prospective and be balanced I enjoy activities over sitting and watching but I have been known to sit in front of the TV and watch football or college basketball all day Im looking for someone who enjoys life and doesnt take themselves too seriously ADDITIONAL TIPS from Matchcom Our anonymous remailer Re Matchcom Youve Got Mail Hello AgainHi Paul Well lets see where do I start first of all I am in the process of moving to Denver I am still in Scottsdale AZ I am moving next week to the Littleton area It been very annoying to move around this time but I had to I took a position with the Denver Federal Center and they wanted me to start asap So I decided to make the move About me I am yrs old very ambitious I work very hard but love to play hard as well I feel that lifes to short and to be stressed out is just not worth it I like to be around professional people but they have to have a great sense of humor and like to have fun Someone with no personality is just not for me Ive been told I have a very warm personality I pretty much can get along with everyone It surprises people but I never could understand that They usually say that if they didnt know me thats not what they would think I actually like to do about anything once My philosophy on what I like to do is its not what we do its who we do it with I do enjoy very much to go out and experience the nicer restaurants I enjoy the theatre and musicals I can go on and on So if I havent answered your question Do ask DO you have any other pics to share Marlene From To Subject Matchcom Youve Got Mail Hello Again Date Fri Dec Marlene Thanks for the email Ok Ill tell you more Im I live in Broomfield but work downtown Im currently looking to sell my place in Broomfield and move west into the area around Golden Maybe Lookout Mountain or Genesee Broomfield is ok when youre married which I was for years now divorced two but a little far from everything when youre single Athletic but only competitive when provoked How am I doing so far I moved to Colorado from Texas San Antonio in and I dont think Im going back although Im in the energy business which is run primarily out of Houston TX No pets or kids due to the fact that I travel somewhat frequently for my job and pleasure Well at least the travel and pets part the kids part is for other reasons which Im sure you can imagine I like to ski but prefer the summer better And finally if I get this job Ill work very hard to insure this company remains profitable and loyal to its customers Oh sorry I got off on a tangent So now its your turn tell me more Paul ADDITIONAL TIPS from Matchcom Our anonymous remailer will strip away your real email Re Matchcom Youve Got Mail Hello AgainHi Paul I am finally here in Denver The move was sooo hectic but I am glad its all over with Unfortuntely if it wasnt for the job I would not of moved around this time Its really weird that I am away from the family around this time Hope your holidays are going well Marlene From To Subject Matchcom Youve Got Mail Hello Again Date Wed Dec Hello I thought Id write and see how you are doing How is the move going Im still working on sending additional pictures We had our company Christmas party last weekend and I thought pictures would be taken They werent so Ill have to come up with another plan The snow has been falling in the mountains here lately and the skiing is turning out to be quite good Do you ski Ive only been up a couple of times this year but Id like to go more I think I may try and go here towards the end of this week Hows the weather in AZ I bet its great this time of year I wanted to get back in touch so write back when you get a chance Paul ADDITIONAL TIPS from Matchcom Our anonymous remailer will strip away your real email address so that it will NOT appear in the From line You may also contact this person from their
